  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nStar Atlas Town Hall #38\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of the latest Star Atlas Townhall.\nStar Atlas : Townhall Recap : The Leak End Ep. 5\nPockThePirate posted a video recapping the Star Atlas Townhall.\nLET’S GO SAGE!!! 4/26\nGladiator posted a video of his review of the Star Atlas Townhall.\nSTAR ATLAS Major Town Hall Recap – 426, Scavenger Hunt & LOOT\nMetaVerse Explorer posted his recap of the Star Atlas Townhall.\nMetaverse Nomads #91 Star Atlas Town Hall Summary\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their latest Star Atlas live stream.\nSAGE: ESCAPE VELOCITY – EVERYTHING WE KNOW!\nAephia published an article about SAGE: Escape Velocity.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #76\nAephia published their latest Star Atlas newsletter.\nSTAR ATLAS #177 Scavenger Hunt Prep & FREE SHIPS!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about getting ready for the Star Atlas scavenger hunt.\nStar Atlas Escape Velocity, what I need to know\nOCG Thor posted a video about the upcoming SAGE: Escape Velocity.\nStar Atlas Revolutionary Technology Reaches Escape Velocity: Real-time Fully On-chain Space Movement on Solana\nStar Atlas published an article announcing SAGE: Escape Velocity.\nStar Atlas : Escape velocity Tutorial – SAGE\nPockThePirate posted a tutorial of SAGE: Escape Velocity.\nGalia Merchants — Star Atlas’s First Community Licensed Merchandise Store Launches\nThe Hologram published an article about a Star Atlas merchandise store.\nTL;DR —The Star Atlas Town Hall Recap You Won’t Read\nThe Hologram published an article recapping the Star Atlas Townhall.\nThe Ultimate Star Atlas Escape Velocity Guide — Updated with NEW Loot Table!\nThe Hologram published an article as a guide to SAGE: Escape Velocity.\nStar Atlas Escape Velocity Crashes! Deploy Airbags\nOCG Thor posted a video about how to handle the crashes in Escape Velocity.\nSTAR ATLAS SCAVENGER HUNT BEGINNER GUIDE!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of a beginner guide to the Star Atlas scavenger hunt.\nSCANNING FOR LOOT IN STAR ATLAS – GAME IS LIVE ON SOLANA!\nThe Club posted a video about scanning for loot in Star Atlas.\nSTAR ATLAS – Movement Test and Review\nAtlas Theory posted a video reviewing the Star Atlas movement test.\nAMAZING Tip’s to find LOOT | SAGE Star Atlas\nGladiator posted a video with tips for finding loot.\nStar Atlas launches into Escape Velocity, Putting Solana to the Test\nKrigs published an article about testing Solana by Escape Velocity.",
